document_data.name: House Shraiee
document_data.mainbody: '''Shraiee''' was an [[elven]] house in the City of Song, [[Myth Drannor]], before its fall in the [[Weeping War]] in [[714 DR]].
document_data.History: House Shraiee was known for making extremely high-quality musical instruments. Alongside Houses [[Lharithlyn]] and [[Tlanbourn]], the Shraiee family was considered one of the best instrument makes of Myth Drannor.
